OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man who had to flee his home in      
OL,6, Swansea after he was caught up in the  
OL,7, Mayhill riot six months ago has said he
OL,8, is "shocked" and "disappointed" no-one 
OL,9, has been prosecuted.                   
OL,11,FFather-of-two Adam Romain left Waun-Wen
OL,12,FRoad because he no longer felt safe    
OL,13,Fafter "yobs" torched cars and threw    
OL,14,Fbricks at houses on 20 May.            
OL,16,FPolice made 37 arrests but no-one has  
OL,17,Fbeen charged while they await a Crown  
OL,18,FProsecution Service (CPS) decision.    
OL,20,FThe CPS has been asked to comment.     
